      "writtenOn": "2021-06-21T19:29:09Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sorry are you referring to a single case that is both msaa_render_to_texture and no barrier support? If we are in that case we have to break up the render pass right? Won\u0027t this do that or am I missing something?",
